author: Matt Walsh
description:
Matt Walsh heads straight into the belly of the beast — California — to call out Democrats for sacrificing female athletes on the altar of gender ideology. He’s testifying in support of AB 844, a California bill that would keep men out of women’s sports. Titles, scholarships, and the basic dignity of girls are on the line — and Walsh is making it clear: the insanity ends now.
